# Azure TypeScript (api/ + orchestration/)

- **Auth:** Entra JWT via `jose`; app roles `CollisionSpike.User` / `CollisionSpike.Superuser` (legacy `CollisionSpike.Admin` still accepted).
- **Postgres:** connect as non-owner `cespk_app` (RLS enforced); per-connection role via libpq `-c app.role=staff`.
- **Deploy:** esbuild bundles to `deploy/api/main.cjs` and `deploy/orch/main.cjs`. Keep the **import.meta.url** banner or the host registers 0 functions. Ship `node_modules`. See [docs/azure/deploy.md](docs/azure/deploy.md).
- **CORS:** platform setting on the Function App (`az functionapp cors`), not `host.json`.
- **Feature gates:** Function app-settings (`PDF_MAPPER_ENABLED`, `ENRICHMENT_ENABLED`, `BOX_*`, etc.) — live values in the registry only.
- **Read-only triage:** dispatch **azure-diagnostician** before mutating live resources. Mutations → **azure-integration-engineer** + playbooks.
